CORRECTION OF ERRORS ATTRIBUTED IN THE

Submitting the documents referred to below, does not rule out the possibility of a judicial investigation if the judge deems it necessary.

Required documents

Application form duly completed and signed;

Original birth certificate of the concerned issued by the place of birth (to be translated into Arabic in the case issued in a foreign language);

A copy of the concerned birth certificate containing such error;

If available, official documents containing the identity used by the concerned such as (school certificates, a copy of the identification card, a copy of the passport, a work certificate ....);

For further information about this service, please do not hesitate to contact us

